videos.description: Hawks get out to a 6-0 lead after Trae Young lobs it up to Clint Capela for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Hawks get off to hot start with Trae's lob to Capela) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hawks get off to hot start with Trae's lob to Capela

videos.description: The Hawks lose the ball as it ends up with Seth Curry who cashes the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Seth Curry splashes the 3 off the broken play) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Seth Curry splashes the 3 off the broken play

videos.description: Trae Young takes advantage of Ben Simmons' foul trouble as he knocks down the long 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ice Trae splash 3 with Simmons looking on) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ice Trae splash 3 with Simmons looking on

videos.description: Tyrese Maxey comes off the screen and throws a dart to Dwight Howard for the dunk plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tyrese Maxey whips pass to Dwight Howard for and-1 jam) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tyrese Maxey whips pass to Dwight Howard for and-1 jam

videos.description: Trae Young flips in the shot high off the backboard and gives a little shimmy before the 76ers call timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Trae Young shimmies after floater off glass) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trae Young shimmies after floater off glass

videos.description: Trae Young continues to dominate the first half as he finds Clint Capela with the impressive touch pass.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Trae's sweet touch pass leads to easy dunk) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trae's sweet touch pass leads to easy dunk

videos.description: Seth Curry come out of halftime scorching hot as he nails three shots from long range.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Seth Curry hot from deep to start 3rd quarter) 2021/06/18 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Seth Curry hot from deep to start 3rd quarter

videos.description: John Collins hauls in the lob and obliterates the rim with a dunk on Joel Embiid.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Collins soars to throw down on Embiid) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Collins soars to throw down on Embiid

videos.description: Onyeka Okonwgwu meets Tobias Harris at the rim for the impressive block.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Okongwu gets the impressive block on Harris) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Okongwu gets the impressive block on Harris

videos.description: Ben Simmons denies Trae Young's 3-point attempt. Then it's Joel Embiid's turn as he swats Young's layup attempt.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Simmons, Embiid not letting Young get anything) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons, Embiid not letting Young get anything

videos.description: John Collins and Joel Embiid get into a scuffle after an offensive foul on Embiid.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Collins, Embiid scuffle leaks off the court with double techs assessed) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Collins, Embiid scuffle leaks off the court with double techs assessed

videos.description: Trae Young hits wild 3 at the shot-clock buzzer, cutting the 76ers' lead to one late.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Are you kidding, Trae Young?) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Are you kidding, Trae Young?

videos.description: The lights go out at State Farm Arena as the 76ers inbound the ball in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lights go out on the 76ers in Atlanta) 2021/6/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lights go out on the 76ers in Atlanta

videos.description: Joel Embiid tips in the bucket with just over a minute to go to seal the game for the 76ers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid's tip shot late helps 76ers force Game 7) 2021/06/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid's tip shot late helps 76ers force Game 7

videos.description: The 76ers avoid elimination as they take down the Hawks to force a Game 7 back in Philadelphia.

videos.headline: 76ers win heated test with Hawks to force Game 7
